### Register User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "VS Code User",
  "email": "vscode@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "vscode@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Create Todo - MANUAL TOKEN (Replace YOUR_TOKEN_HERE)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "Test from VS Code",
  "description": "This todo was created from VS Code REST Client",
  "priority": "high"
}

### Get All Todos - MANUAL TOKEN
GET http://localhost:3000/api/todos
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Todos with Pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/api/todos?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE